<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.2">
<l>nāntakañ caṅkutaṇṭu nāṇolic cārṅkan tiruccakkara</l>
<l>mēntu perumai yirāmaṉaiyi rukkumiṭan nāṭutirēl</l>
<l>kāntaḷ mukiḻviralcī taikkākik kaṭuñcilai ceṉṟiṟukka</l>
<l>vēntar talaivaṉ caṉakarācaṉ taṉvēḷviyilkaṇ ṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you seek the dwelling place of Rama</l>
<l rend="indent">with the greatness of bearing the Nāndaka [sword],</l>
<l rend="indent">the conch, the staff, the Śārṅga with resounding bowstring,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the divine discus,</l>
<l>there are those who have seen him at the sacrifice</l>
<l rend="indent">of King Janaka, king of kings,</l>
<l>[where he] went to break the strong bow for the sake of Sītā,</l>
<l rend="indent">[her] fingers like the buds of glory lilies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
